title: Juush
description:
## **Headliner:**

### ► **Juush**

[Linktr.ee/itsjuush](https://www.linktr.ee/itsjuush)

From viral remixes of Chris Lake, Fisher, and Shiba San to official releases on Box of Cats and Retail Records, Juush is all about keeping the vibes high, the smiles big, and the vibes on ten. Juush will be making his headliner debut at Bergerac, for our residency night with supporting resident artists from the Dirty Not Sorry crew.
